<h2 style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;">各学院</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;">:</span><br/></h2><p style="text-indent: 43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">学校的建设和发展凝聚着所有</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">江软人</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">的智慧和心血，更离不开每一届毕业生校友的关心与支持。在新形势下，为进一步加强</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">校友工作的开展，</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">促进校友事业进步，助力母校改革发展，推动校友与母校共赢共荣，搭建毕业生与母校沟通桥梁，加强毕业生走向社会后与母校及校友会的联系，及时掌握校友信息，促进母校和校友事业的共同发展，经学校研究决定，在</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">各学院选聘</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">校友工作</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">信息官</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">，现将有关事项通知如下：</span></p><p style="margin-left: 0;text-indent: 27px"><span style="font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">一、</span><span style=";font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">基本条件</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">1、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">学院在职人员。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">2、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">思想品德端正，关心</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">学</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">校事业，关注</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">学</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">校发展；热心校友工作，具有奉献精神和服务意识。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">3、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">交际、组织能力及责任心强。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">4、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">群众基础及综合素质好，在</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">学生</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">中有较高号召力和凝聚力，能积极组织</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">学院</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">同学开展活动。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">5、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">学生工作管理人员优先</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 0;text-indent: 27px"><span style="font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">二、</span><span style=";font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">主要职责</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">1、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">在学院校友会的指导下开展常规工作，积极配合学校校友联络办公室开展工作。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">2、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">建立与各地校友会及行业重点校友定期通报制度，以校友之家网站、期刊等为交流平台，建立优秀校友事迹记录和宣传机制，及时报道学校要闻和校友新动向、新成就，保持学校与校友之间的经常联系。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">3、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">有计划地组织校友返校开展各种活动，校友联谊活动的内容主要包括：通报学校、学院发展近况，介绍校友成长道路，举办各类专题讲座，开展业务洽谈与合作，听取校友对学校工作的建议等等。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">4、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">认真做好校友返校接待工作，做好各项服务和信息收集工作；积极为校友单位招聘培训、信息咨询等牵线搭桥；鼓励校友回母校再深造，做好相关信息及咨询工作；全心全意为校友解决困难和难题；每逢春节、元旦等重大节假日前夕给本学院校友发送电子贺卡或者祝福邮件表达问候，使广大校友充分感受到母校的关怀，使学校发展成果惠及广大校友。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">5、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">积极完善本院校友信息的收集、整理、更新工作；建立、健全各行业重点校友档案库，维持良好的校友关系，有针对性地开展个性化服务；严格遵守信息保密规定，严禁泄露校友信息；做好学院校友数据库与学校校友联络办公室的信息共享和对接工作。</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">6、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">负责学院在校生校友意识培育工作。充分利用新生入学、毕业教育和老校友返校等机会，采取各种形式，培育和增进在校学生的校友意识。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">7、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">认真落实学校校友联络办公室的各项工作安排，及时做好校友活动信息及相关工作动态的汇总、报送和联络工作。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 0;text-indent: 27px"><span style="font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">三、</span><span style=";font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">选任办法及程序</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">1、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">采用个人自荐与学院推荐相结合的方式进行</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">2、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">每学院选送信息官一名</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">，</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">报送</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">校友联络办公室</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">3、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">校友</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">办</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">统一颁发聘书。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 0;text-indent: 27px"><span style="font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">四、</span><span style=";font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">工作要求</span></p><p style="text-indent: 43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">各学院请于</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">202</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">3</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">年</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">9</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">月</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">26</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">日前将</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">《</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">江西软件职业技术大学</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">校友</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">工作信息官</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">推荐表</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">》</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">纸质版报送</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">校友联络办公室</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">(IBM楼101办公室）</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">备案，并将电子版发送至邮箱</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">804532064@qq.com</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">邮件标题：学院名称</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">+校友工作</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">信息官</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">。</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><br/></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">联系人：</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">徐元斌</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:仿宋">电话：</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">17607912375</span></p><p style="text-indent: 43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">附件：江西软件职业技术大学校友信息官推荐表</span></p><p style="text-indent: 43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent: 43px; text-align: right;"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-left: 0px; text-indent: 336px; text-align: right;"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">江西软件职业技术大学</span></p><p style="margin-left: 0px; text-indent: 336px; text-align: right;"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">校友联络办公室</span></p><p style="text-align: right;"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">202</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">3</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">年</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">9</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">月</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">21</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">日</span></p><p><br/></p>